response.overview: A man, determined to win the neighborhood's annual Christmas decorating contest, makes a pact with an elf to help him win. However, the elf casts a spell bringing the twelve days of Christmas to life, bringing chaos to the small, unsuspecting town.
response.tagline: Be careful what you wish for.
response.title: Candy Cane Lane

results.name: A Walk Down Candy Cane Lane: Part I
